_SyslogSlide1Text_:
Launch Cisco DNA Center. Go to "Design" > "Network Settings" > "Network." For each site, add the CX Collector IP as the Syslog Server.

Once this is set, all devices associated with that site will be configured to send syslogs with level Critical to CX Collector.

_SyslogSlide4Text_: Click each site and select all the devices and under action select "Optimal Visibility."
